Ok, my first question to you is exactly what is your definition of an &quot;UBERguild&quot; and who is/are the UBERguilds on our server?  My second question is which UBERguild has been fighting MMDN tooth and nail as you call it?  Surely it isn't Afterlife...this thread is the first that Afterlife has really posted on at MMDN much...can you identify which uberguild has been fighting you and maybe point out a thread or some posts to me this has occurred in?  Also, there are a lot of ways to determine raids...1C1S is the best in my opinion but &quot;the only right way?&quot;  Exactly who said that? There are a lot of ways to do everything.<br>
<br>
